title: NOAA NDFD, Wind speed /direction forecast after Gustav landfall near Lake Charles, LA on Sept 03, USA, Aug 29 2008
name: NOAA NDFD, Wind speed /direction forecast after Gustav landfall near Lake Charles, LA on Sept 03, USA, Aug 29 2008
description:
The point shapefile shows the forecast data for the 3rd of Sep, 2008 after Gustav's landfall near Lake Charles, Lousiana on 2nd Sep, 2008. 
The data was derived from NOAA's National Digital Forecast Database (NDFD).
